<input id="dialog-contact" type="checkbox"/>
<div class="dlg-contact">
	<div class="overlay"></div>
	<div class="dialog">
		<header>
			<label class="close" for="dialog-contact"></label>
			<h1>Me Contacter</h1>
		</header>
		<div class="content">
			<p class="success"></p>

			<form id="contact-form">
				<p>Pour me contacter, veuillez remplir le formulaire ci-dessous<br/>
					<small>Les champs marqu√©s d'une * sont obligatoires.</small>
				</p>

				<p class="errors"></p>

				<input name="name" type="text" maxlength="100" placeholder="Nom complet">
				<input name="email" type="email" maxlength="100" placeholder="Adresse mail">
				<input name="subject" type="text" maxlength="200" placeholder="Objet">
				<textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Message..."></textarea>
			</form>
		</div>
		<footer>
			<button type="button" class="button">Annuler</button>
			<button type="button" class="button" id="js-btn-send">Envoyer</button>
		</footer>
	</div>
</div>